properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 23 at 3:33PM EST until January 26 at 6:00AM EST by NWS Mount Holly NJ
properties.description:
* WHAT...East winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 30 kt and seas 6
to 9 feet expected.

* WHERE...Portions of Atlantic coastal waters.

* WHEN...From midnight Friday night to 6 AM EST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM MIDNIGHT FRIDAY NIGHT TO 6 AM EST SUNDAY
